Similes & Metaphors
---
A metaphor is an opportunity to draw the reader’s attention to something. Use them to pick out a detail that may be useful later. 

- Extended the metaphor to hammer home a point. <%= link ">>>", "./pages/1587951537.leaf" %>
- Keep your similes consistent with the story’s point of view. <%= link ">>>", "./pages/1607654585.leaf" %>

